messages.messageBody:
I'm not sure if any of you are aware, but there is a company called Osprey Publishing that
specializes in military history books. I am currently attempting to persuade them to issue
some books on the Battle of Ueno since I have hardly been able to find any books on the
battle in English. If you have an interest in seeing an English-language book written about
them, please send them an email. You can get their conact info at
www.ospreypublishing.com. Just a few minutes of your time and we might be able to
persuade them to make a valuable contribution to military history students.
